<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 3. Coccidula litophiloides Reitter SEM illustrations, paratype HNHM A body, dorsal B pronotum C head and prothorax, ventral D meso and metaventrite E head ventral. Scale bars: 1 mm (A); 500 µm (B-D); 400 µm (E)." , "Figure 2. Coccidula lepida LeConte SEM illustrations A pronotum B head and prothorax, ventral C meso and metaventrite D elytra dorsal E ventrite 1. Scale bars: 500 µm (A-C); 1 mm (E, D)." , "Figure 9. Coccidula scutellata (Reitter) SEM illustrations A body, dorsal B pronotum C head, ventral D mesoventrite, metaventrite and ventrite 1 E prosternum F ventrites 4 - 6, male G pro-tarsal claw. Scale bars: 1 mm (A); 500 µm (B, D, E); 400 µm (C, F); 100 µm (G)." , "Figure 10. Coccidula scutellata (Reitter) A tegmen, inner B tegmen, lateral C penis, lateral D male genital segment, dorsal E spermatheca F female genitalia G left and right mandibles H maxilla I metendosternite. Scale bars: 500 µm (A-F); 200 µm (G-I)." , "Figure 7. Coccidula rufa (Reitter) SEM illustrations A body, dorsal B pronotum C head and prothorax, ventral D antenna E mesoventrite, metaventrite and ventrite 1 F ventrites 4 - 6, female. Scale bars: 1 mm (A); 500 µm (B, C, E, F); 400 µm (D)." , "Figure 4. Coccidula litophiloides Reitter A tegmen, lateral B tegmen, inner C penis, lateral D spermatheca. Scale bar: 500 µm (A-D)." , "Figure 5. Coccidula reitteri Dodge SEM illustrations, HNHM A body, dorsal B pronotum C head and prothorax, ventral D meso and metaventrite E antenna. Scale bars: 1 mm (A); 500 µm (B-D); 300 µm (E)." , "Figure 1. Immature stages and habitus of adult species of Coccidula Kugelann A C. rufa larva B C. rufa pupa C C. lepida, dorsal D C. lepida, ventral E C. litophiloides F C. reitteri G C. rufa H C. scutellata A, B Gilles San Martin, Wikimedia Commons C, D Danny Haelewaters G, H Udo Schmidt. Scale bars: 1 mm (C-H)." , "Figure 8. Coccidula rufa (Reitter) A tegmen, inner B tegmen, lateral C penis, lateral D male genital segment, dorsal E spermatheca. Scale bar: 500 µm (A-E)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/554378" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/554385" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/554386" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/554383" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/554376" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/554380" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/554379" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/554384" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/554377" .

